Because that's a bit
of a success story.

00:30:35.390 --> 00:30:36.690
&gt;&gt; Armstrong Wiggins: Yes,

00:30:36.690 --> 00:30:40.370
that's VAWA is a big success
story, but it's ongoing.

00:30:40.370 --> 00:30:41.670
&gt;&gt; Carrie N. Lyons: Yeah.

00:30:41.670 --> 00:30:43.030
&gt;&gt; Armstrong Wiggins: And a
lot of challenges that we face

00:30:43.030 --> 00:30:47.640
in the United States
because, as you know,

