00:32:09.520 --> 00:32:13.360
that we have a lot
of good women,

00:32:13.360 --> 00:32:17.040
native women, leading
this fight.

00:32:17.040 --> 00:32:20.090
And I can name many of
them, Terry Henry, you know,

00:32:20.090 --> 00:32:24.470
others who are leading
this fight nationally.

00:32:24.470 --> 00:32:29.350
And so we are just supporting
them, and now working with them,

00:32:29.350 --> 00:32:31.190
helping them fundraising.

00:32:31.190 --> 00:32:36.260
A general worker from our
office is the head of one

