signal we should wrap up.

01:08:25.500 --> 01:08:26.990
But I'd like to thank you
both again for coming out.

01:08:26.990 --> 01:08:28.290
This was wonderful.

01:08:28.290 --> 01:08:29.590
We are so grateful
to have you here.

01:08:29.590 --> 01:08:30.890
And I'd also like
to thank everybody

01:08:30.890 --> 01:08:32.290
for spending time with us today.

01:08:32.290 --> 01:08:34.090
Thank you.

